# Cursor Rules for Video Teacher Project

## Development Tools
- Use Desktop Commander MCP for terminal operations and file management
- Use Playwright MCP for automated testing and browser automation
- Prefer MCP tools over direct terminal commands when available

## Code Style
- Use TypeScript for all new files
- Follow Next.js 15 App Router patterns
- Use ShadCN UI components for consistent design
- Implement proper error handling with custom error classes

## Testing
- Write E2E tests with Playwright for critical user flows
- Use Vitest for unit tests
- Test responsive design on mobile and desktop
- Include accessibility tests
- Prioritize Chrome browser for testing and development
- Test Chrome compatibility first, then other browsers

## Build & Deployment
- Optimize for Vercel deployment
- Use environment variables for configuration
- Implement proper error boundaries
- Follow Vercel best practices

## UI/UX
- Use gradient backgrounds and glass morphism effects
- Implement smooth animations and transitions
- Ensure mobile-first responsive design
- Follow modern design principles

## Performance
- Optimize images and assets
- Use Next.js Image component
- Implement proper caching strategies
- Monitor Core Web Vitals
